<RefNameDiv>
<RefName><command>cdn-sync</command></RefName>
<RefPurpose>
Incrementally synchronize an Red Hat Satellite's RPM repository with Red Hat's CDN RPM repository.
</RefPurpose>
</RefNameDiv>

